verbose_text: One SKCRP, SKCRP14.1, which is downregulated in an antimonial resistant strain, increases antimonial induced apoptosis but protects from miltefosine induced apoptosis [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: SKCRP, SKCRP14.1, which is downregulated in an antimonial-resistant strain, increases antimonial-induced apoptosis
